# File: build files - backup/vendor.css.ab
# Purpose: Backup copy of the vendor CSS bundle preserved from a previous Grunt build
# Dependencies: [vendor.css.ab]

## Overview
A preserved copy of a previous `vendor.css` build artifact stored in the `build files - backup/` directory. Contains the same concatenated minified vendor CSS as the root `vendor.css` (select2, slick-carousel, growl notifications, and other UI library stylesheets), captured at a specific point in time as a rollback reference. Approximately 98 KB.

## Interface
No exports. A reference/archive file not loaded by the running application.

## Dependencies
- vendor.css.ab — the canonical source this was copied from

## Implementation Notes
- This directory (`build files - backup/`) appears to be a manually created backup of build artifacts, not generated by the automated Grunt pipeline
- File size: ~98 KB (compared to the current root `vendor.css`)
- Not referenced by `app/index.html` or any build configuration
- Exists alongside `build files - backup/vendor.js` as a paired backup snapshot
